# vim:ft=plumed
UNITS NATURAL

p: POSITION ATOM=2
doubleWell: CUSTOM ARG=p.x PERIODIC=NO ...
  FUNC=x^4-7*x^2+x+14.14
...
potential: BIASVALUE ARG=doubleWell

opes: OPES_METAD TEMP=1 ARG=p.x PACE=500 BARRIER=14 SIGMA=0.2

PRINT FMT=%g STRIDE=500 FILE=COLVAR ARG=p.x,doubleWell,opes.*

ENDPLUMED

Notice that we are in the highly unrealistic situation in which
we are biasing all the degrees of freedom of the system.
OPES is not meant to handle this and can sometimes 
be slow at converging, see replica 2.
